stringStats.value: Token of Rare Armor Damage Boost V

This token may be traded to Nalicana, the Seer of the Yalain, in Asheron's Castle, in order to spend 10,000 Luminance for 1 Luminous Crystal of Rare Armor Damage Boost V. When used, this gem will increase your Damage Rating by 5 for 3 hours.
A pyreal token marked with intricate runes.  The carvings glow with a faint light.
